p20
aVhave suggested that we need a 70 percent increase
p21
aVin current agricultural practice
p22
aVto meet that demand.
p23
aVGiven that plants are at the base of the food chain,
p24
aVmost of that's going to have to come from plants.
p25
aa(lp26
VThat percentage of 70 percent
p27
aVdoes not take into consideration the potential effects of climate change.
