VI'm going to show you a video
p146
aVof the resurrection process of these three species
p147
aVin that order.
p148
aVAnd at the bottom,
p149
aVthere's a time axis so you can see how quickly it happens.
p150
aa(lp151
V(Applause)
p152
aa(lp153
VPretty amazing, huh?
